{"tid":1415200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位我發夢去左黃大仙集會 有野想講","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:52:48.000Z","uid":191568,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d246a3cc49a1ff5bb42a76fb5d0d3767fc4d71e","tid":1415200,"uid":191568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:21:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">物資好重要 唔好周圍擺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我發夢做左垃圾佬 周圍搵搵散落物資 希望幫到手<br />\n<br />\n我見到泳鏡 頭盔 周圍擺 我唔敢拎 驚d 物資係其他人<br />\n<br />\n最後我發夢記晒散落物資的位置 中間人鍵 話要咩 <br />\n<br />\n最後我唔理件野係邊個 去返所在地點 我即刻拎左上前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外 <br />\n<br />\n港鐵站妹妹仔  雖然你地話夠錢買飛 唔洗收錢<br />\n<br />\n但我都想出一分力 下次我會強行要你收的<br />\n<br />\n唔一定買飛嫁嗎 總有用得著的時候<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你地要加油呀！！</span>"},{"pid":"fbc4fef61b98f11d6ee6f6fc738d5dd556b6bb95","tid":1415200,"uid":191568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:27:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"249d8f612ca2293fa6b4a1ab1c82a0a012f673a6","tid":1415200,"uid":191568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:32:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4fa9aadd24c80879abe08875a2427614aca000d5","tid":1415200,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"想問有冇執到豬嘴"},{"pid":"1d61f7f1de0a6d6be51572484aa33e55e746d1d2","tid":1415200,"uid":191568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fa9aadd24c80879abe08875a2427614aca000d5","tid":1415200,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"想問有冇執到豬嘴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:39:58.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"22b2f01be3b7574e465e6504abffad67746cb70f","tid":1415200,"uid":191568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8dd40cd554dff973b978e57de764841b2721488c","tid":1415200,"uid":191568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":